<p>The student archetype that consistently gets the most value from GLIM Chennai: an engineering background with genuine quantitative interest, 0–3 years (PGDM) or 5+ years (PGPM) of professional experience, clear sector focus on BFSI or analytics, self-motivated enough to pursue certifications and sector knowledge beyond the assigned curriculum, willing to build alumni relationships proactively rather than waiting for the placement cell to create all connections, and realistic about anchoring the first 3–5 post-MBA years in south India. Students who fit this description consistently report the highest satisfaction and land in the top placement quartiles.</p>

